                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Gadla Mäbʿa Ṣǝyon and Miracles of the Saviour of the World worked by
                        ʾabuna Mäbʿa Ṣǝyon are contained also in Maṣḥafa la-tazkāra Madḫāne ʿĀlam
                        “Book of Commemoration of the Saviour of the World” (s.<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESmr016">MR-016</ref>and<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESfbm004">FBM-004</ref>).</note>
                     <note>- Gadla Mäbʿa Ṣǝyon (<locus target="#54rb">54rb</locus> l.8-74va l.3) is
                        assigned for the month Maggābit, s. <locus target="#54r">54r</locus>: ዘአቡነ፡
                        መብዓ፡ ጽዮን፡ ዘይትነበብ በወርኃ፡ መጋቢት ʻOf ʾabuna Mäbʿa Ṣǝyon is read in the month of
                        Maggābitʼ.</note>
                  </msItem>
